<TEI.2><text><body><div1 type="alphabetic letter" n="O" org="uniform" sample="complete"><entryFree key="Oyster" type="main" opt="n"><orth extent="full" opt="n">Oyster,</orth> the animal Ostrea: <bibl n="shak. wiv 2.2.2" default="NO" valid="yes">Wiv. II, 2, 2</bibl>. <bibl n="shak. ado 2.3.25" default="NO" valid="yes">Ado II, 3, 25</bibl>. <bibl n="shak. ado 2.3.25" default="NO" valid="yes">Ado II, 3, 25</bibl> <bibl n="shak. shr 4.2.101" default="NO" valid="yes">Shr. IV, 2, 101</bibl>. <bibl n="shak. lr 1.5.26" default="NO" valid="yes">Lr. I, 5, 26</bibl>. Supposed to contain a precious pearl in its shell: <bibl n="shak. ayl 5.4.64" default="NO" valid="yes">As V, 4, 64</bibl>. <bibl n="shak. ant 1.5.44" default="NO" valid="yes">Ant. I, 5, 44</bibl>.
